agName":"h4","properties":{"id":"Jigoku-Game-Log"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#Jigoku-Game-Log","ariaLabel":"Jigoku Game Log permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","height":"20","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"20"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Jigoku Game Log"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Jigoku Game Log goes into the DOM to extract the game events, omits superfluous information like chat messages, summarises and formats important information, and then sends this newly-produced game log to "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://markdownshare.com"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"markdownshare.com"}]},{"type":"text","value":" to be saved for sharing and saving, for either analysis or sharing war stories with comrades."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h4","properties":{"id":"Challenges"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#Challenges","ariaLabel":"Challenges permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","height":"20","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"20"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Challenges"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Using "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"const"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"let"}]},{"type":"text","value":" gave me errors, so I used "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"var"}]},{"type":"text","value":" throughout. I guess this might be because the script is constantly ongoing and doesn't get garbage collected."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Submitting the game log to markdownshare.com through the fetch API was difficult."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"First, Chrome doesn't allow fetch API from most areas in the extension. It needs to be done in the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"background.js"}]},{"type":"text","value":", so "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"message passing"}]},{"type":"text","value":" needs to be used to get the fetch request to "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"background.js"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Second, I had issues with permissions, with my request not getting sent, with no informative error logs. Turns out, there are several places to add the cross-origin site permissions to."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Third, the API usage example on markdownshare.com showed the use of cURL. What I didn't realise, what that cURL automatically sends the message with "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ContentType:application/x-www-form-urlencoded"}]},{"type":"text","value":" when using the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"-d"}]},{"type":"text","value":" option, so I needed to specify this manually with "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"fetch"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and I also needed to do "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"encodeURIComponent()"}]},{"type":"text","value":" on the text."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h4","properties":{"id":"Results"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#Results","ariaLabel":"Results permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","height":"20","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"20"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Results"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"More than 10 users in the L5R community